"title": "1305: God, activity of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "1305",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>God is not passive or remote from his creation but dynamically involved in all that he has made. In the past, this activity was seen in the history of Israel and in the ministry of Jesus Christ. In the present, God's activity can be seen in the life of believers and of the church.</p>\n<h2>God is active by nature</h2>\n<h3>He actively works out his purposes</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:17\">JHN 5:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num23:19\">NUM 23:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps115:3\">PSA 115:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:4\">PRO 16:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa43:13\">ISA 43:13</a></p>\n<h3>His names reflect his activity and involvement in his people's lives</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen22:14\">GEN 22:14</a> <em>“The LORD Will Provide”</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod15:26\">EXO 15:26</a> <em>“The LORD, who heals you”</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod17:15\">EXO 17:15</a> <em>“The LORD is my Banner”: this title emphasises that God is like a warrior who champions his people's cause</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps95:6\">PSA 95:6</a> <em>“The LORD our Maker”: the Hebrew word used does not refer to original creation but to the way in which God is fashioning a people for himself.</em></p>\n<h3>His word is active</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa55:10-Isa55:11\">ISA 55:10–55:11</a></strong> <em>The Hebrew for “word” can also be translated “deed” or “action”. God's word is not merely a communication of abstract truth but a powerful force active in the world.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:3\">GEN 1:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek37:4\">EZK 37:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek37:7\">EZK 37:7</a></p>\n<h2>God is active in the creation</h2>\n<h3>In making the universe</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:6\">NEH 9:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:1\">GEN 1:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:31\">GEN 1:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:2\">GEN 2:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen5:1-Gen5:2\">GEN 5:1–5:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps102:25\">PSA 102:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos4:13\">AMO 4:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:24\">ACT 17:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev4:11\">REV 4:11</a></p>\n<h3>In sustaining the created order</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps103:19\">PSA 103:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:10-Ps104:17\">PSA 104:10–104:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps107:33-Ps107:35\">PSA 107:33–107:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:28-Matt6:30\">MAT 6:28–6:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:17\">ACT 14:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:11\">EPH 1:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:16-Col1:17\">COL 1:16–1:17</a></p>\n<h3>In bringing about changes in the weather</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job37:10\">JOB 37:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job38:22-Job38:30\">JOB 38:22–38:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job38:34-Job38:35\">JOB 38:34–38:35</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps107:25\">PSA 107:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps147:8\">PSA 147:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:45\">MAT 5:45</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:17\">ACT 14:17</a></p>\n<h3>In the stars and other heavenly bodies</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job38:31-Job38:33\">JOB 38:31–38:33</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:19\">PSA 104:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps147:4\">PSA 147:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:26\">ISA 40:26</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:17\">JAS 1:17</a></p>\n<h3>In the animal creation</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job39:1-Job39:30\">JOB 39:1–39:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job40:15-Job40:24\">JOB 40:15–40:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job41:1-Job41:11\">JOB 41:1–41:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:20-Ps104:27\">PSA 104:20–104:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps147:9\">PSA 147:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:29\">MAT 10:29</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:6\">LUK 12:6</a></p>\n<h2>God is active in Israel's history</h2>\n<h3>In the calling and creation of Israel as a people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod6:6-Exod6:8\">EXO 6:6–6:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen12:1-Gen12:3\">GEN 12:1–12:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod19:3-Exod19:6\">EXO 19:3–19:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:32-Deut4:34\">DEU 4:32–4:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa51:2\">ISA 51:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:6-Ezek16:7\">EZK 16:6–16:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos11:1-Hos11:4\">HOS 11:1–11:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal2:10\">MAL 2:10</a></p>\n<h3>In saving and delivering his people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps106:2\">PSA 106:2</a></strong> <em>This verse introduces a psalm which recounts the history of God's dealings with his people.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod33:16-Exod33:17\">EXO 33:16–33:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam7:7-2Sam7:11\">2SA 7:7–7:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs18:36-1Kgs18:38\">1KI 18:36–18:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps28:8-Ps28:9\">PSA 28:8–28:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps107:2-Ps107:3\">PSA 107:2–107:3</a></p>\n<h3>In judgment</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num25:3-Num25:4\">NUM 25:3–25:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:25\">1SA 2:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam12:16-1Sam12:18\">1SA 12:16–12:18</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam21:1\">2SA 21:1</a></p>\n<h3>In bringing victory in battle</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod14:27-Exod14:28\">EXO 14:27–14:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod17:8-Exod17:16\">EXO 17:8–17:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num21:1-Num21:3\">NUM 21:1–21:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh6:2\">JOS 6:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh10:30\">JOS 10:30</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg7:9\">JDG 7:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg7:22\">JDG 7:22</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:47\">1SA 17:47</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr20:22-2Chr20:23\">2CH 20:22–20:23</a></p>\n<h3>In raising up and sending leaders to the people</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam7:8-2Sam7:9\">2SA 7:8–7:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr24:19\">2CH 24:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth4:14\">EST 4:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer7:25\">JER 7:25</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech7:7\">ZEC 7:7</a></p>\n<h2>God is active in the nations of the world</h2>\n<h3>His rule over the nations</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps22:28\">PSA 22:28</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen11:8\">GEN 11:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:8\">DEU 32:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg2:20-Judg2:23\">JDG 2:20–2:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job12:23\">JOB 12:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps46:8-Ps46:10\">PSA 46:8–46:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps66:7\">PSA 66:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:2\">ISA 41:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:26\">ACT 17:26</a></p>\n<h3>Examples of nations through which God acts</h3>\n<p>Assyria:\n <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:18-2Kgs17:23\">2KI 17:18–17:23</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa28:11\">ISA 28:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs24:10-2Kgs24:14\">2KI 24:10–24:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr36:15-2Chr36:18\">2CH 36:15–36:18</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr36:22-2Chr36:23\">2CH 36:22–36:23</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra1:1-Ezra1:4\">EZR 1:1–1:4</a> <em>Persia</em></p>\n<h2>God is active in human life</h2>\n<h3>He determines the course of human lives</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:28\">ACT 17:28</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:12\">1CH 29:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps8:3-Ps8:4\">PSA 8:3–8:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps75:6-Ps75:7\">PSA 75:6–75:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps139:16\">PSA 139:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:52\">LUK 1:52</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:4\">JHN 1:4</a></p>\n<h3>Examples of God's intervention in human lives</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num22:21-Num22:23\">NUM 22:21–22:23</a> <em>Balaam</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam1:19-1Sam1:20\">1SA 1:19–1:20</a> <em>Hannah</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs5:14-2Kgs5:15\">2KI 5:14–5:15</a> <em>Naaman</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah1:17\">JON 1:17</a> <em>Jonah</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:3-Acts9:6\">ACT 9:3–9:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:1-Acts13:3\">ACT 13:1–13:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:6\">ACT 16:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:10\">ACT 16:10</a></p>\n<h2>God is active in Jesus Christ's ministry</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:38\">ACT 10:38</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:17\">LUK 5:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:20\">LUK 11:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:2\">JHN 3:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:17-John5:19\">JHN 5:17–5:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John9:3-John9:4\">JHN 9:3–9:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:10\">JHN 14:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:19\">2CO 5:19</a></p>\n<h2>God is active through the Holy Spirit</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:2\">GEN 1:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs2:16\">2KI 2:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek8:3\">EZK 8:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek11:1\">EZK 11:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek43:5\">EZK 43:5</a></p>\n<h2>God is active in the church</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:6\">1CO 12:6</a></strong> <em>This verse comes in the context of teaching about the body of Christ and the gifts which the Spirit gives to the church.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor14:24-1Cor14:25\">1CO 14:24–14:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:8\">GAL 2:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:5\">GAL 3:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:10\">EPH 3:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:20-Eph3:21\">EPH 3:20–3:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:6\">PHP 1:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:13\">PHP 2:13</a></p>",
